-> install & autostart dropbox
sudo pacman -S dropbox --needed
~/.config/openbox/autostart
dropbox &

-> XFCE persistent display configuration
create display profile, enable automatic setup
ugly workaround for setting wallpapers with nitrogen: put this in openbox autostart to properly load multi screen wallpapers:
sleep 1 && nitrogen --restore &

-> lightdm: autologin
https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/LightDM#Enabling_autologin
need to set logind-check-graphical=true if it doesnt work

-> rofi: set german keyboard layout
~/.xprofile
setxkbmap de

-> light desktops: volume change notification
https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Volnoti

-> light desktops: use picom compositor
https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Picom
sudo pacman -S picom
configure picom, then autostart
